additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Fabric softeners are not for use on children's sleepwear, or other garments labelled as flame resistant, as they may reduce flame resistance. Keep out of reach of children. Eye irritation: If product contacts the eyes, rinse thoroughly with water. If swallowed: Seek medical advice. Medical Advice: 13 11 26 (Australia) or 0800 764 766 (New Zealand)
